org.gephi.data.properties

Enum PropertiesColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PropertiesColumn>
      • org.gephi.data.properties.PropertiesColumn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<PropertiesColumn>

    public enum PropertiesColumn
extends Enum<PropertiesColumn>
    Enum that define static AttributeColumn indexes, like ID or LABEL. Use these enum to find the index of these columns in node and edge table.

    Get nodes ID column 
     AttributeColumn col = nodeTable.getColumn(PropertiesColumn.NODE_ID.getIndex());

    Author:
    Mathieu Bastian, Martin Å kurla
